	shorttitle = {Phenological Shifts in Lake Ice Cover Across the Northern Hemisphere},
	abstract = {Abstract
            
              Long‐term ice phenology records quantify the effects of climate change on Northern Hemisphere lakes. This study uses lake ice phenological records across a gradient of lake sizes (0.1–31,967.8 km
              2
